<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="47" type="phenology">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="47">Phenology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="47">Flowering and fruiting of this species have been recorded at the very end of the rainy season and the start of the dry season in May and June; thus most plants are leafless during the peak of the flowering period.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
